      'Shakers Sitar StifKarp VoicForm FM BeeThree FMVoices HevyMetl PercFlut Rhodey ' +
      'TubeBell Wurley UGen_Multi UGen_Stereo Chubgraph Chugen FilterBasic FilterStk ' +
